title: What More Can You Take?
itunes:title: What More Can You Take?
description:
On this emotional episode of The Gangster Chronicles, James, Reggie and Alex discuss those that were murdered during their time at Death Row Records, The Los Angeles Rebellion and the aftermath. Did things change after the riot?, What do you think? Hit us up on Instagram @gangsterchronicles to let us know what's on your mind. Support the show.
